can be deduced from every variant of Cardano&#x27;s formula by reduction to a depressed cubic. The variant that is presented here is valid not only for real coefficients, but also for coefficients belonging to any field of characteristic other than 2 or 3. If the coefficients are real numbers, the formula covers all complex solutions, not just real ones.

